parameters.name: 捕食（スライムピストン）+【凌辱】女子高生喘ぎ声5

parameters: \nc<>Saki's body is almost entirely buried inside the pot.

\nc<>What's happening beneath the swarm of tentacles can only be
left to imagination.

\nc<>However, due to her belly swollen as if she's at full term,
one can somewhat guess...

\nc<>The inside of the pot is filled not only with tentacles but
also with a foul smell, sensation, and noise.

\nc<>In a situation where she can hardly see because of the
tentacles, Saki desperately squeezes out her voice.

\nc<Saki>E-enough already, let me out... I'll do anything you say...
Nnah...♥
\nc<Employee>Hmm, perhaps it's about time to take her out.

\nc<>A glimmer of hope shone through what was more a murmur to
oneself than a conversation...

\nc<Employee>The pot is full now. We need to take out the ones that have
grown to a certain size.

\nc<>Once again, amidst the damp and lewd noises, Saki's swollen
belly writhes ominously.

\nc<>Regardless of her own will, the wriggling belly is
disgustingly horrifying...

parameters.name: 捕食３（スライムピストン）+女子高生フェラ8

parameters:
\nc<>The employee forcefully pushes an especially thick tentacle
into Saki's mouth. The tentacle, recognizing the familiar
hole, dives into her mouth in an instant.

\nc<Employee>Eat plenty and give birth to plenty, okay? I have quotas to
meet too...
